name: YouCube (UnrealCraic)
description:
Replace all blocks missing from the big cube as fast as you can by rotating them to the same orientation. Press SPACE to fire it in!

Each cube you complete adds 1 to your multiplier

Each cube has more blocks missing than the previous

Controls are described when you launch the game

have fun!

All sounds obtained from:

https://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music/track/moose

https://freesound.org/
